##Cyprus Under the British
### Cyprus Philatelic Literature

Castle, Wilfrid T.F. - Cyprus
Its Postal History and Postage Stamps
Publisher: Robson Lowe Ltd., London, 1971.
Second edition, hardback, dustwrapper, illustrated, xi + 256 pages.

The best source of information of Cyprus stamps and postal history id the late Rev. Wilfrid Castle's book. This is a classic handbook, covering all aspects of the stamps and postal history of Cyprus. As it is out of print copies can usually be found at Philatelic Literature dealers.



